TITLE: Defining Custom Data Pipeline PHP
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to define a custom data pipeline for a specific Data class by overriding the static `pipeline` method. This allows you to explicitly list the pipes that will process the data for this particular data object, chaining standard or custom pipes using the `through` method.
